Command: Say
Syntax: SAY <message>

This is the basic command for communication.

Example:

say i like cheese

Output:

You say, "I like cheese."

Note the automatic formatting.

A few emoticons are supported, if you use them at the end of the command.

Example:

say i like cheese :)

Output:

You smile and say, "I like cheese."

Note that extra spaces will be removed.

See also: WHISPER, SAYTO
